                                    commodi quam. Beatae animi deleniti magni porro cumque ipsam debitis
                                    quod?Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ab
                                    veniam maxime rem sequi quos? Illo aspernatur perspiciatis voluptates possimus,
                                    commodi quam. Beatae animi deleniti magni porro cumque ipsam debitis
                                    quod?Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ab
                                    veniam maxime rem sequi quos? Illo aspernatur perspiciatis voluptates possimus,
                                    com?</span>
                                <span> ao confirmar</span>
                                </span>
                            </label>
                            <input type="checkbox" value="Confirmar" class="confirmar-button" id="licenca" required>

                        </div>

                        <button id="confirmar">Confirmar</button>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </form>

            <!-- </div> -->




        </main>


    </body>

</html>